metadata.name: The First Elder
metadata.description:
70 custom and curated (icons) depicting The Seventy Elders of Hinnom, the original trailblazers that led the Hinnomites to the promised land. 
 Every elder plays a huge part in the history of the universe. Become an elder to shape the landscape of Middle America and the events of the Book of Mark, as well as becoming a recurring (icon) in the series.
